<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Message Board Menu</title>
</head>
<body>
<!--Heading of the page-->
<h1>Welcome to the Message Board</h1>
<!--Include Icon for the h1-->
<!--List of Dynamically generated Topics-->
<div class = "message-join-sections">
    <h2>Add a New Topic</h2>
    <p>Join other young people like yourself to lend a voice to this topic. You have a voice, use it.</p>
    <p>Engage. Share ideas.</p>
    <a href="/listtopic.co"><button type = "button" class = "but" >Join Conversation</button></a>
</div>
<!--Choose from available Topics-->
<div class = "message-action-sections">
    <img src = "" alt = "">
    <h2>Join a conversation!</h2>
    <p>Browse a list of existing topics and choose to read from others or join on-going conversations
        you are passionate about.</p>
    <p>Feel free, it's a safe space.</p>
    <a href="/listtopic.co"><button type = "button" class = "but" >Choose a Topic</button></a>
</div>
<!--Exit the application-->
<div class = "message-action-sections">
    <img src = "" alt = "">
    <h2>Feel free, take a break!</h2>
    <p>We miss you already, but understand you love to share the lovely conversations here with other
        friends. Enjoy! </p>
    <p>We can't wait to have you back!</p>
    <a href="/exit.co"><button type = "button" class= "but" >Quit</button></a>
</div>
<!--Develop a Quit Application Information to Show the User-->
